ed="T" n="0869c15"/><persName key="A013602">釋神智</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000013594">婺州義烏</placeName>人也，俗姓力。力氏之先，黃<lb
ed="T" n="0869c16"/>帝臣牧之後。漢有魯郡相<persName key="A013603">力歸</persName>，因官居<placeName key="PL000000021539">兗</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0869c17"/>遂為<placeName key="PL000000020229">魯</placeName>人也。祖考皆田畯，而以朴素相㳂。<lb
ed="T" n="0869c18"/><persName key="A013602">智</persName>少有貞操，懇樂捨家，就雲門寺<!--找不到此地--><persName key="A013604">惟孝</persName>為<lb
ed="T" n="0869c19"/>師。<date key="j20245772024941" from-iso="+0831-01-01" to-iso="+0831-12-31">年十二</date>，一食斷中，持大悲心呪，應法登<lb
ed="T" n="0869c20"/>戒，峻勵恪勤。俄屬<date key="j20282682030170" notAfter-iso="+0846-04-25" notBefore-iso="+0841-02-08">會昌</date>滅法，<persName key="A013602">智</persName>形服雖殊，<lb
ed="T" n="0869c21"/>誓重為僧，磨不磷而涅不淄，于時見矣。<date key="j20304612031609" notAfter-iso="+0850-04-03" notBefore-iso="+0847-02-10">大<lb
ed="T" n="0869c22"/>中初年</date>，復道。巡遊<placeName key="PL000000013376">暨陽</placeName>，考于禪室，且曰：「營<lb
ed="T" n="0869c23"/>廷之魚，潛于藪澤，宜哉。此處<persName key="A013602">吾</persName>之藪澤也。」恒<lb
ed="T" n="0869c24"/>呪水盃以救百疾，飲之多差。百姓相率，日給<lb
ed="T" n="0869c25"/>無算，號<persName key="A013602">大悲和尚</persName>焉。<date key="j20304612035056" notAfter-iso="+0859-09-10" notBefore-iso="+0847-02-10"><name>大中</name>中</date>，入<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName>，時昇<lb
ed="T" n="0869c26"/>平相國<persName key="A003624">裴公休</persName>預夢<persName key="A013602">智</persName>來，迨乎相見欣然。<lb
ed="T" n="0869c27"/>相國女<anchor xml:id="beg0869007"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>即</sic><corr>郎</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0869007"/>鬼神所被，<persName key="A013602">智</persName>持呪，七日平復。遂<lb
ed="T" n="0869c28"/>奏請院額曰<placeName key="PL000000012326"><name>大中</name>聖壽</placeName>，仍賜左神策軍鐘<lb
ed="T" n="0869c29"/>一口、天后繡㡧、藏經五千卷。<persName key="A003624">裴君</persName>為書殿額。<pb ed="T" n="0870a" xml:id="T50.2061.0870a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0870a01"/><persName key="A013602">智</persName>以<date key="j20450322045061" notAfter-iso="+0887-01-31" notBefore-iso="+0887-01-02">光啟丙午歲十二月</date>，終于<placeName key="PL000000013605">東白山</placeName>，春秋<lb
ed="T" n="0870a02"/>六十八，法臘四十八。遷座歸<placeName key="PL000000013376">暨陽</placeName>南山入<lb
ed="T" n="0870a03"/>塔焉。</p>
